make mrproper
make allmodconfig
make prepare
make kernelrelease 
	2.6.18-ga5fa393b
vi MAINTAINERS
make prepare
make kernelrelease
	2.6.18-ga5fa393b-dirty
So it wrks for me.
Can you provice a few more details what steps you do when you see it failing.
